text: Branded Man is the fourth studio album by Merle Haggard featuring The Strangers. It was released on 28 August, 1967 through Capitol Records and went to number 167 in the United States. In 2003, it was ranked #484 on the Rolling Stone 500 Greatest Albums of All Time. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1967 albums Category:Capitol Records albums Category:Merle Haggard albums
title: Branded Man
